{"tid":2516131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少林寺竹林慘遭摧殘　冇品遊客攀爬刻字　逾500年石碑都遭殃","createTime":"2021-05-04T12:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T12:51:54.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab3fb515777c12582fd773ac0cf0340ad47aad4","tid":2516131,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uIWNg3lOs1zg7DhswsvUAhr6C4M=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/05-04-2021/t_66be04224d044c00bdbf460c922e5e05_name_30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuIWNg3lOs1zg7DhswsvUAhr6C4M%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%2F05-04-2021%2Ft_66be04224d044c00bdbf460c922e5e05_name_30.jpg&h=f86e4761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n今年五一假期，內地「前借後取」駁長假，催谷民眾外遊消費，引發「報復性旅遊潮」，各地景區人滿為患，也出現不少亂象。河南登封少林寺景區就被遊客淹沒，寺內一片竹林更慘遭缺德者摧殘破壞。<br />\n據內媒報道，昨日（3日）在河南登封少林寺景區內，數十名大人帶着小孩遊竹林，但他們未有好好欣賞林中景致，反而不停爬竹子，還吊在上邊盪鞦韆，有竹子因而被折斷。從現場畫面可見，爬上竹子的不僅有小孩，還有健壯的成年人。有遊客表示，因為小時候擅長爬樹，就想再試一試，「健健身」。<br />\n此外，很多竹子上還被刻了字：某某某到此一遊、某某與某某1314&hellip;&hellip;還有小孩爬完竹子當場開始刻字，大人也沒有阻攔。<br />\n還有幾個孩子在古碑上刻畫，畫完後又用手塗抹，在古碑上留下一道長長的白疤。碑文落款顯示，此碑可能已有500多年歷史。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210504/YTDPGGXI4NFK5M6HMDYXEFDHPE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210504%2FYTDPGGXI4NFK5M6HMDYXEFDHPE%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=ec3ff861\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210504%2FYTDPGGXI4NFK5M6HMDYXEFDHPE%2F&h=476b1721\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210504/YTDPGGXI4NFK5M6HMDYXEFDHPE/</a>"},{"pid":"c2cb005f846a6dda5cd626b2a74a0985d15b9a1b","tid":2516131,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"如果全部人都冇品<br />\n咁仲叫唔叫冇品？"},{"pid":"beae0aced1